TAKE 1 PC 1 SERVER AND 1 SWITCH
CONNECT THE THREE
ASSIGN IP ADDRESS TO DESKTOP
IP Address: 192.168.1.2
Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0
Gateway: 192.168.1.1

ASSIGN IP ADDRESS TO SERVER
IP Address: 192.168.1.3
Subnet Mask: 255.255.255.0
Gateway: 192.168.1.1

CLICK ON SERVER AND OPEN SERVICE TAB YOU WILL SEE HTTP HTTPS AND FTP 
FIRST TURN ON THE HTTP AND TURN OFF THE HTTPS AND FTP AND GO TO PC AND OPEN WEB BROWER AND TYPE http://192.168.1.3 DO SAME FOR HTTPS AND FTP(ftp 192.168.1.3)
